0.11.0 (2017-05-05)

 - Add setting to narrow possible authors to porject members (#22).

0.10.0 (2017-03-18)

 - Add option to set original author of issue for users with new
   "Set original author" permission.


0.9.4 (2017-03-14)

Enjoy work of @yoshida3669 this time!

 - Keep original author of the issue if issue was moved to another project
   and they are not a member of it.


0.9.1 (2016-10-31)

First bugfix release thanks to Ivan Kvetkin!

 - It is now possible to change author to any active user in the project.
   Previously only user assignable to issue could be selected.


0.9.0 (2015-11-06)

Initial public release.
